Source: fsm-core
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/Nirajkashyap/fsm/tree/main/packages/database-src-extension/fsm_core

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-fsm-core
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-fsm-core
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION-pgmq, postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-jsonschema
Description: Finite state machine toolkit for PostgreSQL
  fsm_core provides finite state machine primitives inside PostgreSQL using
  SQL schema objects. It requires ltree, pgmq, and pg_jsonschema.
